Who destroyed much of the Islamic Empires in the Medieval Ages?;The Mongols destroyed the Islamic Empires in the Medieval Ages, and the Christian Crusaders made it weaker.
Who was Genghis Khan?;He was the leader of the Mongols.
What was the purpose of the Crusades?;Christians wanted to be able to visit the Holy Land and to win the Holy Land back from the Muslims.
What was the Reconquista?;It was a 700 year war the Spanish Catholics fought against the Muslims in Spain. The Spanish won in 1492.
